categories: Category:Imperial Navy officers of the Galactic Empire

nodes.text: This Imperial commander served on the Super Star Destroyer Executor during the Galactic Civil War. Some months after the Battle of Hoth, Darth Vader ordered this commander to set the Executor's course for the Dagobah system, where he learned Luke Skywalker was located.

This character appears in the Infinities comic Star Wars Infinities: The Empire Strikes Back, and thus is non-canon. The story represents an alternative scenario for Star Wars: Episode V The Empire Strikes Back in the event that Luke Skywalker dies from his wampa encounter on Hoth.
